  "number": 2196,
  "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/pull/2196",
  "title": "Make search function provide a better API",
  "body": "This implementation offers:\r\n - a full helper to modify the parameters before sending the request\r\n - all the other search function (searchOnce, searchForFacetValues)\r\n - compatibility with async code (no oops effect)\r\n\r\n*warning*: This also contains a modification of the slider to be extra sure that we'll never update the state unnecessarily https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch.js/commit/8b7a6eb60fe879c0fa9841931dffbe2d91d1b24b\r\n\r\nFixes #1924 \r\n\r\n - [Deployed version with 2sec lag of all search requests](http://flashy-art.surge.sh/): test the async\r\n - [Nominal version](http://bite-sized-birth.surge.sh/): just a simple search function, this also serve to test the perf of the search function mechanics\r\n - [without any search function implementation](http://busy-snail.surge.sh/): let you test the slider modification by itself\r\n",
